# CUAD Contract Review Pipeline — Cursor Rules

- Explicit type hints on every function
- async/await only — no blocking calls (use asyncio.to_thread for sync I/O)
- Pydantic models for all data contracts between agents
- No global mutable state
- All file I/O in try/except with errors appended to state.errors
- Never load the entire data.zip into memory at once — stream one contract at a time
